gov.loc.repository.bagit.verify.impl

Class ParallelManifestChecksumVerifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.loc.repository.bagit.utilities.LongRunningOperationBase
      • gov.loc.repository.bagit.verify.impl.ParallelManifestChecksumVerifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cancellable, ProgressListenable, FailModeSupporting, ManifestChecksumVerifier, ManifestVerifier

    public class ParallelManifestChecksumVerifier
extends LongRunningOperationBase
implements ManifestChecksumVerifier, FailModeSupporting
    A verification strategy that verifies a bag's payload using multiple threads. The number of threads is initially set to the number of CPUs, but may be manually set using #setNumebrOfThreads(int).
